Package org.jarpatch

Class Summary
JarContent maintain a view of a Jar content.
JarPatch build a patch zip that contains the difference between a newJar from an oldJar.
JarPatchTask An Ant task for building zip patch, corresponding to the difference between 2 jar files.
Main A simple main around the JarPatch.
